summary:
Door to enter is just outside Markarth, just look up and you will see the island. or you can simply fast travel to it.

The mod only requires the .esp and the newest version of Skyrim.
descriptionHtml: This is just a little house that ive started making... it is floating above markarth and there is a picture of how to get up there...door right underneath it. not finished yet... wanted to get this out and see what people think about it so far. Added an arena in the house, with 3 working merchants (Blacksmith, Enchanter, Alchemist)
author: Brendan00999
